Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}中獎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特獎 全家溫泉旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做的好呀 白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太厲害了 是特獎啊 特獎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜同學真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 招待券五人份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個是溫泉導遊手冊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恭喜囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難得中獎了 表現的再高興一點怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.84,0:00:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}高興一點？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 相當開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像是這上面寫的溫泉哪裡都能去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是白夜中獎的 那就去白夜想去的溫泉怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 這裡 想去這裡看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}UMA溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}UMA溫泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有這溫泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 這個漢字不是這麼讀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那這裡怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}UMA之鄉？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\c&H30272F&\an7\fad(150,0)}歡迎來到未確認的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前在電視上有出現過唷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}據說有出現很多UMA所以很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\c&H30272F&\an9}你也有可能和它們浪漫相遇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像是尼斯湖水怪的恐龍之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}槌之子和大蜥蜴之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像有點讓人懷疑是不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 這裡就好！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就選這個UMA之鄉 請務必！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白不是怕UMA還有外星人之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過就是因為這樣才吸引人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以說是對未知 未確認的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘿～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.64,0:01:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這麼輕易就決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明是家族旅行也沒忘記帶上我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為媽媽的工作很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}餘下一人份不用也很浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊～ 真期待呢 UMA之鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會有什麼樣的UMA在等著我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是這樣的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想在溫泉裡應該不會有恐龍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也很期待喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.26,0:02:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和小紅還有真白碳一起洗澡什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想要是紅緒不在的話我會更期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最近都沒能跟小紅一起洗澡 姊姊覺得好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是個讓裸體對話文化復活的機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且當然是和真白碳一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是想像體溫就上升了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒姊好像也很期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她在想什麼大概都能想像的到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H3D3943&}歡迎來到UMA之鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到達啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&HC1DAD4&\3c&H858784&}古老UMA資料館     {\c&H302C42&\3c&H474A77&}民宿UMA      {\c&H5644A4&\3c&HFFFFFF&}飯店UMA一番館     {\c&H4D474D&\3c&HFFFFFF&}旅館UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H191D45&}UMA{\c&H1D235D&}仙貝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6A84A0&\an7}UMA糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 真的都是UMA耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全把觀光地當作賣點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔 UMA這麼快就出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當地特產的吉祥物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這麼說的話確實在手冊裡面出現過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}魔法的UMA 魔法UMA醬對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難得遇到了 來拍張紀念照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}噫 什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和真白碳拍紀念照成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然旅行會氣氛高漲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想這跟平常一樣吧
Comment: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an7\fs30}喜翠莊擴建了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 好漂亮的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺好有神祕的氛圍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起看景色還是先洗澡吧 洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在我們就去泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}換裝太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來吧 讓我們手牽著手潛入眼花繚亂的泡澡世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來吧 來吧來吧來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要去換衣服 你先去泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}外面有露天溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快換好來唷！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}洗澡的話不是那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:04:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我還沒有魯莽到和紅緒一起洗澡的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 真舒爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然和家裡的泡澡不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像要冒出什麼東西的氣氛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的很適合作為UMA之鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過是不是實際存在還不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那個啊 我稍微調查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結果真的有很多疑似的目擊情報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像是尼斯湖水怪的恐龍 好像會在剛剛那個湖水出現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有森林裡有大蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有毛茸茸的怪獸和謎之生命體之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不、不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這應該也是吸引客人的宣傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過這氣氛真的感覺會出來什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等去探險吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就只是這樣洗澡太浪費了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姊姊大人不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來吧 快來吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可愛的妹妹們唷～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嚇嚇她們吧 小小的驚喜對於對話來說是必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用擔心紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}UMA看到她跑還來不及呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話是這麼說 但是難得大家一起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}卻只有姊姊在別的地方有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}該不會真的是恐龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這怎麼說都不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅 真白碳 終於找到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人家找好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是從哪裡出來的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡和外面的溫泉是相連的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我從那裡潛水過來的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姊姊大人也很擅長游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是那種程度的問題嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然森林裡面好黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係 已經全副武裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像電視上的探險特輯一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像是特意向旅館的人借來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白醬 果然在緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:07:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的 因為終於能遭遇UMA了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真由良好像不怎麼害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊哈哈 因為和大家在一起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用帶那麼多裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會在你身邊的 沒關係～的～說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和紅緒在一起的話 在別的意義上很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是什麼聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道是大蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是毛絨絨的怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我過去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼啊 是烏鴉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 真白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姊姊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣下去的話 就會和小紅她們失散了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和真白碳獨自相處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳 等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}找姊姊大人的時候和真由良失散了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}地圖和指南針都在真白那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}往哪裡走才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}無論發生什麼 我都會保護小紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以不要這麼輕易就說出這種話……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}旅館的方向在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…這裡是哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊呀呀 好像撞到哪裡壞掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都怪紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用那麼可怕的形象追我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我來負起責任 我們結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算一輩子生活這個森林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也會一直照顧真白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個身影 和人類差不多大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會吧…真的是UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道真的是UMA嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:09:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道會是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姊姊大人 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是小紅她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白 已經可以放心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看啊 是我們住的旅館哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好厲害啊白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}方向感太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真由良
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我還想去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 找到了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}醒來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看看看看啊 那個 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會吧 應該是雲的影子之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨晚的那個到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然是UMA了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}絕對是UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是拍到照片就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是UMA嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜怎麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白那樣說的話 我想也是UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 這裡也有UMA的報導
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨夜 湖邊又出現了類似UMA的神秘蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}目擊者的A先生證言看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有在樹林間跳來跳去的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不是真白和姊姊大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼我們被當作UMA對待了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這也是紅緒的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我來負起責任結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用擔心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我把這裡變成我們的樂園給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請你在這裡和UMA生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
